    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cyber Courier 2088</strong> is a cyberpunk sci-fi courier game where you can be a <strong>sky taxi</strong> driver transporting passengers and goods in a crazy low-poly world.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278530/extras/77fbedc8ce32c8b5c91432d15d8fcc86.avif?t=1735996622\" width=552 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start out on foot cleaning up the city, then hover up in a space taxi and  <br>enjoy transporting people and goods from place to place some lawful some not so lawful <br>missions.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278530/extras/1f83043570299c4724aeb28e51563226.avif?t=1735996622\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278530/extras_big/1f83043570299c4724aeb28e51563226.avif?t=1735996622 width=800 height=206 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Transport</strong> people and packages within the city</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Earn Credits</strong> and buy weapons and items.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Navigate</strong> Sky Highways (in the full game)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tow</strong> Stranded Vehicles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Clean</strong> up the City</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Avoid</strong> local authorities <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278530/extras/1d88bf5231b069d626a9d9c54f2a191d.avif?t=1735996622\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278530/extras_big/1d88bf5231b069d626a9d9c54f2a191d.avif?t=1735996622 width=800 height=142 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The Demo is limited to one City.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278530/extras/0407730e66617fa1d80d01b375ff5822.avif?t=1735996622\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278530/extras_big/0407730e66617fa1d80d01b375ff5822.avif?t=1735996622 width=800 height=164 /></span>The <strong>Demo</strong> is in a early <strong>alpha</strong> state.<br><br><strong>Latest Updates:</strong><br>Hoverboard - Test it now !!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want to make suggestions at this phase?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278530/extras/c5b75e51d16fae390e98d39461f25d50.avif?t=1735996622\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278530/extras_big/c5b75e51d16fae390e98d39461f25d50.avif?t=1735996622 width=800 height=194 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Then <strong>join</strong> our <strong>Discord</strong> =&gt; See <strong>Steam Links <br> </strong>Weather you call it a Cyberpunk  CyberCab, CyberTaxi, Cyber Courier game...<br>be the ultimate transporter in the universe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
